#

Orange and Spinach Salad

10 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing blend of sweet oranges and fresh spinach, drizzled with a light dressing for a burst of flavor.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • oranges: 2, peeled and segmented
  • red onion: 1/4, thinly sliced
  • almonds: 1/4 cup, sliced
  • feta cheese: 1/3 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
